<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading" id=3D"slots-payouts-by-venue">Slots Payouts =
by Venue</h2>



<p>Slot machines <a href=3D"https://playtoday.co/blog/guides/how-do-slot-ma=
chines-work/">are programmed to return a specific amount to the players</a>=
. As we already mentioned, the payout percentages differ between states, bu=
t they also change when you compare online with brick-and-mortar casinos.</=
p>



<p>Online casinos will have fewer overhead expenses, as they won=E2=80=99t =
have to spend anything on space, servers, dealers, and other staff, equipme=
nt, and lighting. Therefore, <a href=3D"https://playtoday.co/blog/stats/how=
-much-do-online-casinos-make/" data-type=3D"post" data-id=3D"4283">online v=
enues can afford</a> to have a higher payout for slot machines.</p>



<p>On the other hand, the chance of an online casino turning out to be a sc=
am is much higher, as they are not as closely regulated as land-based estab=
lishments.</p>



<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading" id=3D"what-is-rtp">What Is RTP?</h2>



<p>The payout percentage is often referred to as <a href=3D"https://playtod=
ay.co/blog/guides/return-to-player/">=E2=80=9Creturn-to-player=E2=80=9D or =
RTP.</a> This theoretical number represents how much money wagered on a slo=
t machine will be paid back to players over time. It=E2=80=99s important to=
 note that this number does not necessarily reflect the casino=E2=80=99s pa=
yout for slot machines during a single gambling session.</p>



<p>To understand what RTP means for gamblers, you have to know how casinos =
calculate these percentages. These percentages are achieved when casino dev=
elopers spin the virtual reels thousands of times and compare the money inv=
ested against the prizes won.</p>



<p>Therefore, an RTP of 94% doesn=E2=80=99t necessarily mean the player wil=
l get $94 back for every $100 he puts in the machine. The average slot mach=
ine payouts are calculated over a high number of spins, and all of the mone=
y prizes, including multi-million jackpots, are counted as =E2=80=9Creturns=
.=E2=80=9D</p>



<p>Therefore, some players will lose their money, others will break even, a=
nd some will profit. RTP is used in other forms of gambling as well. If you=
 need advice on RTPs in sports betting, for example, you can read about it =
in our guide.</p>



<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading" id=3D"slot-machine-volatility">Slot Machine =
Volatility</h2>



<p>Volatility or variance can be equally important as RTP rates. The volati=
lity of a machine tells you how often it gives money back. For some players=
, this stat can be of more use for their game than a slight difference in a=
 casino=E2=80=99s payout percentage.</p>



<p>A machine with lower volatility is going to be better for novice players=
 who would like to get more of their money back in smaller sums so they can=
 continue playing. Those looking for bigger prizes should seek out casinos =
and machines with higher volatility, as they will offer them a chance for l=
arger jackpots, although such payouts don=E2=80=99t come very often.</p>



<p>Even though casinos don=E2=80=99t advertise volatility nearly as much as=
 they do RTP, you can still estimate which slot machine most likely has a l=
ower or higher volatility rate.</p>



<p>Machines with significant jackpots usually have higher volatility, as th=
ey pay out less often, but their prizes will be higher. On the other hand, =
if the expected winnings are more moderate, that means the machine is less =
volatile.</p>



<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading" id=3D"range-variance">Range Variance</h2>


<div class=3D"wp-block-image">
<figure class=3D"aligncenter size-large"><img fetchpriority=3D"high" decodi=
ng=3D"async" width=3D"1160" height=3D"663" src=3D"https://playtoday.co/wp-c=
ontent/uploads/2022/08/slot-machine-payout-1160x663.png" alt=3D"slot machin=
e payout" class=3D"wp-image-8003"></figure>
</div>


<p>Slot machine payout will also vary in accordance with the game=E2=80=99s=
 outcome range. It is usually thought that slot machines with lower denomin=
ations have a higher RTP rate and will be a better choice for those who wan=
t to play longer.</p>



<p>In the end, the actual payout rate will have to do a lot with the popula=
rity of a certain machine. A slot machine that gets played often will pay o=
ut more prizes in the end because the number of spins will be higher and, t=
herefore, closer to the ideal RTP range. This holds even if the entry price=
 for playing is higher.</p>



